The,TV,API,is,the,interface,for,a,comprehensive,television,database,Users,can,get,information,on,tens,of,thousands,of,TV,shows,and,over,a,million,episodes,The,TV,API,s,primary,source,of,data,is,TheTVDB,which,is,matched,against,data,from,Guidebox,to,provide,a,more,comprehensive,set,of,episode,thumbnails,and,TV,show,artwork,as,well,as,data,on,where,an,episode,or,TV,show,can,be,watched,online,official,sources,only,The,TV,API,can,be,accessed,using,RESTful,calls,to,retrieve,data,in,either,XML,or,JSON,format,The,TV,API,is,now,part,of,Guidebox,Please,see,the,profile,at,api,guidebox